query: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT C.NUNOTA) AS notas_distintas, SUM(ISNULL(I.QTDNEG,0)) AS qtd_total_neg, SUM(ISNULL(I.VLRTOT,0)) AS valor_total FROM [SANKHYA].[TGFITE] I JOIN [SANKHYA].[TGFCAB] C ON C.NUNOTA=I.NUNOTA AND C.CODEMP=I.CODEMP WHERE I.CODPROD = 3680 AND C.STATUSNOTA='L' AND COALESCE(C.DTENTSAI,C.DTNEG) BETWEEN '2025-12-01' AND '2025-12-31 23:59:59'
originalQuery: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT C.NUNOTA) AS notas_distintas, SUM(ISNULL(I.QTDNEG,0)) AS qtd_total_neg, SUM(ISNULL(I.VLRTOT,0)) AS valor_total FROM [SANKHYA].[TGFITE] I JOIN [SANKHYA].[TGFCAB] C ON C.NUNOTA=I.NUNOTA AND C.CODEMP=I.CODEMP WHERE I.CODPROD = 3680 AND C.STATUSNOTA='L' AND COALESCE(C.DTENTSAI,C.DTNEG) BETWEEN '2025-12-01' AND '2025-12-31 23:59:59'
